@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="mb-4">
    <h1 class="h3 mb-1">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <div class="text-muted small">Last updated: Sep 20, 2025</div>
    <p class="mt-3">We respect your privacy. This page explains what information we collect, how we use it, and the
        choices you have.</p>
    <div class="alert alert-light border-0 p-3 mb-0">
        This policy applies to your use of this website and related services ("Services").
    </div>
    <hr />
</div>

<h2 class="h5">Information we collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Account details you provide (name, email, and password).</li>
    <li>Booking and payment-related information when you purchase tickets.</li>
    <li>Event interactions (pages viewed, searches) to improve the experience.</li>
    <li>Technical data such as IP address, device, and browser information.</li>
    <li>Cookies and similar technologies (see “Cookies” below).</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">How we use your information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>To create and manage your account.</li>
    <li>To process orders and deliver tickets.</li>
    <li>To send transactional emails (order confirmations, updates).</li>
    <li>To operate, maintain, and improve the Services.</li>
    <li>To detect, prevent, and address fraud or abuse.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">When we share information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>With payment processors to complete your transactions.</li>
    <li>With event organizers for events you book, as needed to fulfill your order.</li>
    <li>With trusted service providers who help us run the Services.</li>
    <li>When required by law, regulation, or legal process.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Data retention</h2>
<p>We retain personal information only as long as necessary to provide the Services and for legitimate business needs
    (such as accounting), or as required by law. We may anonymize data for analytics.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Your choices and rights</h2>
<ul>
    <li>You can access and update basic account information in your profile.</li>
    <li>You may request deletion of your account, subject to legal or transactional requirements.</li>
    <li>You can opt out of non-essential communications where available.</li>
    <li>You can control cookies through your browser settings.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Cookies</h2>
<p>We use necessary cookies to enable core functionality (e.g., login, checkout), and optional cookies to help us
    improve the site. You can disable cookies in your browser, but some features may not work properly.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Security</h2>
<p>We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information. However, no method
    of transmission or storage is 100% secure.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Changes to this policy</h2>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. If changes are material, we’ll provide notice by updating the “Last
    updated” date above. Your continued use of the Services means you accept the updated policy.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Contact</h2>
<p>If you have questions about this policy or your data, please contact our support team.</p>